-- Post vendor invoices from spreadsheet to SAP.
-- Version: 1.0

Open workbook "data/invoices_batch_feb.xlsx".
In sheet "ToPost", treat range A1F200 as table Invoices.

Use system "SAP-Portal" version "2026.1".
Log in as credential "svc_ap_bot".

For each row in Invoices:
    Go to page "Create Vendor Invoice".
    Enter "VendorField" = row.VendorId.
    Enter "AmountField" = row.Amount.
    Click "PostButton".
    Extract DocNumber from field "DocumentNumberField".

Export Invoices to "output/posting_results_2026-02-11.xlsx".
Log out.
